"<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Weekly Allergy Sheet</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{font-family:'Roboto Mono',monospace;font-size:8pt;color:#000;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;print-color-adjust:exact;padding:5mm 5mm;}
